These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, march
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, blues
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
There 2 different types of food: orange, kale
1. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
3. the fan of blues is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Birthday      | june  | march   |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | rock   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Food     | orange | kale    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, card-games
2 different games are played: billiard, monopoly
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing billiard is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby          | photography     | card-games |
| Game   | monopoly | billiard  |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate         | sprite     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, avocado
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, funk
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the person eating artichoke is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Food    | avocado     | artichoke |
| Music-Genre         | funk | r&b    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire         | action    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
House: cape-cod, cottage
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, february
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, nurse
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the cottage house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the nurse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| House          | cottage   | cape-cod  |
| Birthday         | april | february     |
| Job   | scientist  | nurse         |

