.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
City: colone, venice
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, blue
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| City      | colone | venice       |
| Food           | papaya      | grapefruit     |
| Color   | blue       | brown   |
| Pet           | frog          | chinchilla |

