.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
There 2 different types of food: tomato, strawberry
City: rome, san-francisco
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating strawberry is the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Food           | strawberry | tomato    |
| City   | rome       | san-francisco |
| Beverage           | mirinda         | 7up    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

