2 different pets are kept: goat, snake
1. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Cigar      | oliveros    | old-henry   |
| Color          | white     | ebony |
| Job           | electrician | dancer     |
| Pet   | goat       | snake     |

