1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the wooden house is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
