.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, ivory
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Sport         | volleyball        | tennis |
| Color         | amber          | ivory     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks        | rock-climbing     |

 